OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome early sunshine but
OL,6,Fbecoming cloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,7,Freaching Orkney towards midday and
OL,8,FShetland this afternoon. Risk of some
OL,9,Fheavy, perhaps thundery, rain across
OL,10,FOrkney later this afternoon. Mainly
OL,11,Flight southwesterly winds turning more
OL,12,Fsoutheasterly.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FCloudy with occasionally
OL,15,Fheavy and perhaps thundery rain this
OL,16,Fevening, clearing away southeast
OL,17,Fthrough the early hours. The rest of
OL,18,Fthe night remains cloudy but largely
OL,19,Fdry. Freshening southeasterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
