OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA rather cloudy start but
OL,6,Fsunny spells developing through the
OL,7,Fmorning. Remaining dry through the
OL,8,Fafternoon but cloud increasing again
OL,9,Fin the evening. Winds becoming a
OL,10,Fmainly light northerly.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,13,Fmorning Saturday with occasional rain
OL,14,Fbut afternoon brighter. Rain spreading
OL,15,Feast overnight then clearing early
OL,16,FSunday, then the rest of Sunday and
OL,17,FMonday breezy with sunny spells and
OL,18,Fshowers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
